videos.headline: Grier to Jennings for 53-yard TD
videos.description: QB Will Grier connects with Gary Jennings for a 53-yard touchdown to put the Mountaineers on the board.

videos.headline: West Virginia intercepts Brewer's pass
videos.description: Baylor's Charlie Brewer pass bounces off the chest of his receiver and Mountaineers' Keith Washington is there to take it.

videos.headline: West Virginia collects 2nd interception
videos.description: Mountaineers' Toyous Avery Jr. intercepts Bears QB Charlie Brewer and returns it 32 yards into Baylor territory.

videos.headline: Sills hauls in 42-yard catch
videos.description: Mountaineers' David Sills V climbs the ladder and grabs a Will Grier pass for a 42-yard gain.

videos.headline: Grier connects with Sills for 25-yard TD
videos.description: Will Grier threads the needle and hits David Sills V for a 25-yard touchdown to extend the Mountaineers' lead to 20-0.

videos.headline: Sills grabs and goes for a 65-yard TD
videos.description: Will Grier throws an over-the-shoulder pass to David Sills V for a 65-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Pettaway bursts for a 33-yard TD
videos.description: Martell Pettaway waits for the hole and erupts for a 33-yard touchdown to give the Mountaineers' a 34-0 lead.

videos.headline: Grier punches in a 1-yard TD
videos.description: On a QB sneak, Will Grier drives in a 1-yard touchdown to put the Mountaineers up 41-0.

videos.headline: Bush erupts  for a 79-yard run
videos.description: Tevin Bush turns on the jets for a 79-yard run that sets up a 1st-and-goal for the Mountaineers.

videos.headline: Fleeks runs in for a 2-yard TD
videos.description: Baylor's Josh Fleeks carries in the 2-yard run to put the Bears on the board.

videos.headline: Fleeks runs in for a 2-yard TD
videos.description: Baylor's Josh Fleeks carries in the 2-yard run to put the Bears on the board.

videos.headline: Jennings catches 2nd TD of the night
videos.description: Mountaineers QB Jack Allison finds a wide-open Gary Jennings for a 36-yard touchdown, his second of the night.
